---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="The Savvy Granny's affiliate disclosure and how this site earns from product recommendations."
>
  <article class="container page">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: June 2026</em></p>
    <p>
      The Savvy Granny is reader-supported. Some of the links on this website are
      <strong>affiliate links</strong>, which means that if you click one and make a
      purchase, I may earn a small commission — <strong>at no additional cost to you</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>
      As an Amazon Associate, I earn from qualifying purchases. I may also participate in
      other affiliate programs with stores and brands I trust.
    </p>
    <p>
      I only recommend products I genuinely use, love, or believe will be useful to you.
      The commissions help keep the recipes on this site free. Thank you so much for your
      support — it truly means a lot. 💛
    </p>
    <p>
      Questions about this disclosure? Please <a href="/contact">get in touch</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="muted"><em>This is a standard starter disclosure. It's a good baseline, but it isn't legal advice — once your affiliate programs are set, we can tailor it.</em></p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page { max-width: 700px; padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 2rem; }
  .page h1 { font-size: 2.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .page p { font-size: 1.05rem; }
</style>
